ARC is authorized under the Appalachian Regional Development Act of 1965 (
40 U.S.C. 1-405
), as amended, to serve the Appalachian region. ARC grants are handled in accordance with the ARC Agreement which applies to all ARC grants administered by the Agency. Therefore, a separate Project Management Agreement between the Agency and ARC is not needed for each ARC grant.
